        "content": "## Send Email\nIt will send Bio AI and Blood Report to each member.\nEach member has their own blood_report_url and bio_ai_report_url.\nExpects: { notification_id, members: [{ first_name, email, blood_report_url, bio_ai_report_url }] }",
